events.name: 憩いの場所を取り戻せゴート

parameters:
Goat of the Bulk Gang: 'Hahaha, so you made it back
safely!'

Mage Relm: I didn't hear anything about it turning into a
battle!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Don't get angry, mage. As a token of
gratitude, let the warriors of the Bulk Gang carry the wood
for you.

Priestess Sophia: Is it possible for the warriors to be
stationed here? The villagers are troubled by the harassment
from the nobles.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Leave it to the Bulk Gang, which is
no different from institutionalized thieves, to deal with
the nobles. We won't let the nobles do as they please!

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, it's fun to say anything, isn't
it?

Goat of the Bulk Gang: I believe that I owe you all that
much.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: If anything happens, feel free to
rely on the Bulk Gang at any time!

Thief Nora: I smell something strange... unease, fear...
that smell is coming from Goat-san.

Mage Relm: We're people who have nothing to do with that!
Now, let's go back to Irini Village.
Clea: Alright, let's go report to Mr. Gala.

events.name: 憩いの場所を取り戻せ並列実行
